{"tid":1709483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毅進仔指罵穿校服的中學生唔讀書","createTime":"2019-11-12T01:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T07:35:45.000Z","uid":42188,"like":379,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"6b229b2ad9094beabec8996075ef14adb8517382","tid":1709483,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"西鐵天水圍站連續第2日於繁忙時間停止服務。早上7時許，有市民於西鐵天水圍站往紅磡方向月台爭執，有人阻礙幕門關閉，列車無法駛離車站。有港鐵職員到場處理，但被市民包圍，要求解釋為何列車未能駛走，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n接近早上8時，約30名防暴警員持盾牌進入月台範圍，有防暴警進入列車，帶走1名與在場市民爭執的中年男子，以及1名OL。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有防暴警員於車站大堂截查3名穿校服的學生，查看他們的身份證，大罵他們「垃圾」、「唔讀書」。有市民欲行近拍攝，即被喝止「港鐵唔畀影相」，企圖阻礙拍攝。"},{"pid":"4dfa0cba96f0a58640993db392e3463938968a1d","tid":1709483,"uid":29138,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:47:37.000Z","msg":"呵呵"},{"pid":"d7e2c4c27854588451d90c8b6615ef7aa3b7924d","tid":1709483,"uid":33618,"like":295,"dislike":2,"score":293,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:53:22.000Z","msg":"自己讀唔成書嘅人就最鍾意話人唔讀書"},{"pid":"cdb40c76816a99fc0299331c5addef00d4863f69","tid":1709483,"uid":52090,"like":116,"dislike":0,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:55:04.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書做狗果D，話番有學識嘅人轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1e50d9291102c88ebdc49339490e8f778ef470","tid":1709483,"uid":104833,"like":151,"dislike":0,"score":151,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毅進精英會考幾分先入到"},{"pid":"827fa501de441991196097ea3d7f38c850024ca5","tid":1709483,"uid":69037,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"邊個話港鐵唔比影相"},{"pid":"71284050fc641e0ac9a4629b239abc7dbd556ff1","tid":1709483,"uid":338632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:58:30.000Z","msg":"懇請大家花5分鐘睇下<br />\n<br 